ents_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"## Summary:\n\nA CRLF Injection attack occurs when a user manages to submit a CRLF into an application. This is most commonly done by modifying an HTTP parameter or URL.\n\n## Steps To Reproduce:\n\nNavigate to this URL\n█████:\n```\n┌──(azab㉿kali)-[~]\n└─$ curl -i ███████ \nHTTP/1.1 307 Temporary Redirect\nDate: █████ █████████ GMT\nContent-Type: text/html\nContent-Length: 164\nConnection: keep-alive\nServer: nginx\nLocation: ████████\nSet-Cookie: CRLF_Injection_By_ze2pac\n\n\u003chtml\u003e\n\u003chead\u003e\u003ctitle\u003e307 Temporary Redirect\u003c/title\u003e\u003c/head\u003e\n\u003cbody\u003e\n\u003ccenter\u003e\u003ch1\u003e307 Temporary Redirect\u003c/h1\u003e\u003c/center\u003e\n\u003chr\u003e\u003ccenter\u003enginx\u003c/center\u003e\n\u003c/body\u003e\n\u003c/html\u003e\n```\n\n## Impact\n\nXSS, Open Redirect, HTTP Response Splitting... etc.","weakness":{"id":69,"name":"CRLF Injection"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[],"allow_singular_disclosure_at":null,"vote_count":13,"voters":["khairy0x","g3ksec","zy9ard3","0xoroot","shreyaschavhan","shubham_srt","haoshokunoo","shivammusic","alexanderpetree","salmananu","and 3 more..."],"severity":{"rating":"low","author_type":"Team"},"structured_scope":{"databaseId":368104,"asset_type":"WILDCARD","asset_identifier":"*.banfieldassets.com","max_severity":"critical"},"abilities":{"assignable_team_members":[],"assignable_team_member_groups":[]},"is_exploit_agent_supported?":false,"is_linear_agent_ui_supported?":false,"summaries":[{"id":469595,"category":"team","content":"A CRLF injection vulnerability was present in the website ██████████. This vulnerability occurs when a website or application fails to properly sanitize or encode user-supplied data that contains carriage return and line feed (CRLF) sequences. The attacker can leverage this vulnerability to inject malicious headers or conten